{"tid":1054811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★露宿男倒斃通州街公園　遺體舁送殮房途中再遇車禍","createTime":"2019-03-10T06:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T11:31:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe30404aca24acc1829af84260a722bc215ce6c","tid":1054811,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"深水埗通州街163號通州街公園，今早(10日)6時32分，一名50餘歲男子被發現昏迷小食亭附近，救護員接報到場，證實男子已氣絕身亡。警方到場調查，在現場發現水樽及紙巾等個人物品，相信死者在上址露宿，初步相信案件無可疑，惟死因有待剖驗，正設法聯絡其家人助查。<br />\n<br />\n至早上8時09分，死者的遺體由黑箱車舁送殮房途中，現場下着大雨，當駛至旺角道近上海街交界時，黑箱車疑在燈位前收掣不及，撞向前面一輛外賣電單車，以致南亞裔鐵騎士墮地，手腳受傷。救護員接報到場，為傷者包紮後送院，黑箱車上的司機及仵工俱無恙，警方正調查意外原因。至於死者的遺體則由另一輛黑箱車到場舁走，繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190310/bkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190310%2Fbkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Hs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=3b7bfb85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190310/bkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"32d607cc43953d4a625b5e6456c9e0ef99d08b9b","tid":1054811,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190310/photo/bkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190310103803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190310%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190310073147997-0310_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190310103803&h=30f2b904&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d8e145c69f2e7d60145827154c9148bc0d8151c","tid":1054811,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405e58a5a9375036f990c4239f802f1e84325c5e","tid":1054811,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:03:43.000Z","m